ome.smuggler.core.convert

Interface SourceReader<S,T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CryptoSourceReader, JsonInputStreamReader, JsonSourceReader, JsonStreamReader, MessageBodyReader

    public interface SourceReader<S,T>
    Reads a value V from a data source S. For example, S could be an input stream and the value V could be de-serialised from the stream. Or V could be the body of a message fetched from a queue S.
    See Also:
    SinkWriter
